org.janusgraph.core

Interface JanusGraphVertexProperty<V>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.apache.tinkerpop.gremlin.structure.Element, Idfiable, JanusGraphElement, JanusGraphProperty<V>, JanusGraphRelation, org.apache.tinkerpop.gremlin.structure.Property<V>, Removable, org.apache.tinkerpop.gremlin.structure.VertexProperty<V>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractVertexProperty, CacheVertexProperty, FulgoraVertexProperty, StandardVertexProperty

    public interface JanusGraphVertexProperty<V>
extends JanusGraphRelation, org.apache.tinkerpop.gremlin.structure.VertexProperty<V>, JanusGraphProperty<V>
    JanusGraphProperty is a JanusGraphRelation connecting a vertex to a value. JanusGraphProperty extends JanusGraphRelation, with methods for retrieving the property's value and key.
    Author:
    Matthias Bröcheler (me@matthiasb.com);
